Cookies:
Cookies are small text files that can be used by websites to make a user's experience more efficient. The law states that we can store cookies on your device if they are strictly necessary for the operation of this website. For all other types of cookies, we need your permission. This site uses different types of cookies. Some cookies are placed by third party services that appear on our pages.
Cookies In Use:
We use Cookiebot to manage cookie consent, cookie monitoring, and cookie control. Once a month Cookiebot performs an automated cookie audit of our website.
