International transfers
We may transfer, process or store personal data about you in countries other than your own, which may not have the same data protection laws as your country. When we transfer your personal data to other countries, we will protect that information as described in this privacy notice. Whenever we transfer personal data outside of the EEA, the UK or Switzerland, we take legally required steps to make sure that appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your Personal Data. This includes the use of EU Controller-to-Processor Standard Contractual Clauses (SCCs).
Links to other websites
You should also be aware that where you link to another website from the SilverCloud® by Amwell website, that SilverCloud® by Amwell has no control over that other website. Accordingly, SilverCloud® by Amwell cannot guarantee that the controller of that website will respect your privacy in the same manner as SilverCloud® by Amwell.
Data security
We are committed to ensuring that your information is secure. In order to prevent unauthorised access or disclosure, we have put in place suitable physical, electronic and managerial procedures to safeguard and secure the information we collect online.
SilverCloud® by Amwell maintains
ISO 27001:2013 certification
.
Retention of Personal Data
Personal Data shall be retained only in accordance with the Data Retention requirements of SilverCloud® Privacy Policy.
